    "en": {
      "title": "Important message for the people of Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to a statement issued by the National Water Supply and Drainage Board, an 18-hour water supply ban will be implemented in many areas including Colombo from 8 am tomorrow (3) to 2 am on Sunday.",
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board has informed that this water supply interruption will be in effect due to the essential repair works of the electrical infrastructure for the Ambatala Hydroelectric Station.",
        "According to this, the water supply restriction will be enforced in the areas under Colombo, Dehiwala-Kalkisai, Kota, Kaduwela Municipal Councils and in the areas under Maharagama, Boralaskamuwa, Kolannavai Municipal Councils.",
        "Also, water supply ban will be enforced in the areas under Kottikawathai - Mulleria Pradeshiya Sabha, Rathmalanai and Katupethi. (R)"
      ],
